.TH XIL\-VOICES "1" "2026\-04\-05" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-voices
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-voices
[-h] [--category CAT [CAT ...]] [--search TEXT] [--id VOICE_ID] [--verbose] [--json] [--update-cast CAST_JSON] [--dry-run]
.SH DESCRIPTION
List ElevenLabs voices with enriched metadata

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-category\fR \fI\,CAT [CAT ...]\/\fR
Filter by category: premade cloned generated professional

.TP
\fB\-\-search\fR \fI\,TEXT\/\fR
Case\-insensitive substring filter on name or description

.TP
\fB\-\-id\fR \fI\,VOICE_ID\/\fR
Show full detail for a single voice ID

.TP
\fB\-\-verbose\fR, \fB\-v\fR
Print all fields for each voice

.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output results as JSON array

.TP
\fB\-\-update\-cast\fR \fI\,CAST_JSON\/\fR
Back\-fill role and language_code in a cast JSON from API voice metadata

.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
With \-\-update\-cast: show changes without writing the file

